  "_comment": "Constructive-journalism editorial signals. Used to rank GOOD, solution-oriented information up and doom/outrage/clickbait down. Tunable without code changes. The master switch is BOARDWIRE_CONSTRUCTIVE_MODE (env) or constructive_mode below.",
